		        	<p>Are you hungry? Craving some delicious food? Looking for a good restaurant? Maybe you are in the mood for a juicy meal? No matter what kind of meal you have in mind, <b>HungryCuisine</b> is ready to prepare it for you. <b>HungryCuisine</b> exists for serving you, your family and your friends. Since 2020, HungryCuisine has been the go-to diner for residents of Dhaka, Bangladesh. Our diner serves breakfast all day, in addition to wholesome and flavorful dining options for lunch and dinner. From <b>Khichuri</b> to <b>Kacchi</b>, <b>Chowmein</b> to <b>Ramen</b>, <b>Pizza</b> to <b>Pasta</b>, <b>Fried Chicken</b> to <b>Beef Steak</b>, you’ll find all kinds of hearty meals prepared fresh at <b>HungryCuisine</b>. While everything on the <b>HungryCuisine’s</b> delicious lunch and dinner menus are always cooked to perfection, there are a few standout dishes that can not go without special mention: "Our <b>Mutton Kacchi</b>" - make with perfection and juicy muttons; "<b>Shrimp Noodles</b>" served in our unique style, with lemon and butter drizzled over the dish; "Our <b>T-Bone Steak</b>" - my personal favorite, can be served in either our homemade red or white sauce. Sounds delicious, right? <b>HungryCuisine</b> is open daily from 8 a.m. to 11 p.m. We are here to serve you the best food around, whenever you’re looking for a great restaurant in Dhaka, Bangladesh.</p>
